{"tid":1365501,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"不可以胡亂告 總可以盲著報 人何苦要奶著中央去做","createTime":"2019-07-25T16:03:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T23:42:38.000Z","uid":183576,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3baf198fc4c83245e9ece1871788870bd21d5d67","tid":1365501,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:03:25.000Z","msg":"還未戒掉 朱sir帶給我 那動魄驚心<br />\n還未成熟得撤了佢便無憾<br />\n寧為它曬到頭暈 做個有痛覺的人<br />\n為那中央的惡行 願意比枯草敏感<br />\n<br />\n還未正視 只能站起 領教你的椒煙<br />\n還未麻木得吃夠了便無事<br />\n明白糾察有定時 但勇武夠也不遲<br />\n在這香港得救前 齊頭衝刺<br />\n<br />\n她傷了還未報 他走了還未老<br />\n人難得只因玻璃牽上亂暴<br />\n未會信甚麼釋放等於不告<br />\n流離著對世界說他未在逃<br />\n不可以胡亂告 總可以盲著報<br />\n人何苦要奶住中央去做<br />\n就以血肉之軀去擋煙遮雨<br />\n虔誠地去犯錯 民心 跳得很燥<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一次改，希望唔會誤入教會或者九唔搭八<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724d74059f50e8cf99026fda185d10817ce3a426","tid":1365501,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:04:06.000Z","msg":"邊間教會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965b1ab5fbb5c39ac6e8293070c249af45aecc8e","tid":1365501,"uid":266879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:05:56.000Z","msg":"留意   鐵路手制用法<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HYSpsB2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHYSpsB2.png&h=4be9f38d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc546ec1f11cc238e9ba3101dde1e9ba39b0d846","tid":1365501,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"724d74059f50e8cf99026fda185d10817ce3a426","tid":1365501,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:04:06.000Z","msg":"邊間教會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2